Package com.kuka.roboticsAPI.sensorModel

Contains classes for describing sensors.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDataRecorder
    Enables recording of data in a file.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CartesianForceTorqueInformation
    Provides information of the Cartesian Force and Torque of a device.
    CartesianPositionInformation
    Provides information of the Cartesian Position of a device.
    JointTorqueInformation
    Provides information of the joint torques of a device.
    RecorderConfiguration
    Provides information about the configuration of the IDataRecorder.
    RecorderConfigurator
    A configurator which can be used to create a RecorderConfiguration for the IDataRecorder.
    StartRecordingAction
    Class to start data recording according to a trigger action.
    StopRecordingAction
    Class to stop data recording according to a trigger action.
    TorqueEvaluator
    Class for calculation of maximum absolute torque statistic.
    TorqueStatistic
    This immutable class contains torque statistic data over a period of time.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AngleUnit
    Enumeration to select the unit of an angle.

Package com.kuka.roboticsAPI.sensorModel Description

Contains classes for describing sensors.
This element is an undocumented internal feature. It is not intended to be used by applications as it might change or be removed in future versions.
